imdb.plot outline: Celebrity fitness trainers lead morning viewers through fun and energetic workouts. A variety of Podfitness trainers will be rotated to give the audience a workout similar to their one-on-one training with their own celebrity clients. The show includes an assortment of fitness and nutrition tips, as well. Our goal is to encourage the viewer to get active and feel good.
